# quantum_singularity.rq4d
# Copyright RomanAILabs - Daniel Harding

# --- STEP 1: INITIALIZE THE VOID ---
ALLOC 4

# --- STEP 2: CREATE THE SEED ---
# Put Qubit 0 into Superposition (Hadamard Rotor)
H 0

# --- STEP 3: FOLD THE MANIFOLD (ENTANGLEMENT) ---
# Chain the superposition through the other 3 qubits
# This creates a 4-way maximally entangled GHZ State
CNOT 0 1
CNOT 1 2
CNOT 2 3

# --- STEP 4: TRIGGER THE SINGULARITY ---
MEASURE
